      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like im stuck in this endless loop... every time i think i finally got my life together or found a rhythm that works, i just end up right back at zero. it’s the same mistakes, the same loneliness, the same feeling that i'm just failing at being a person. i'm so tired of trying to fix something that's just fundamentally broken.",
