      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about small steps though. i've tried the small steps. i've tried the \"reframing\" and the therapy and the routine. but the loop is stronger than me. it feels like no matter how much i fight, the outcome is always the same result. it's like i'm running on a treadmill that's just going to keep going until i collapse. it feels so pointless to keep running.",
